# Design brainstorm

For an Alto/Epic task, show the estimated scope and the opt-out before editing. Ask exactly one clarifying question per turn until the scope, constraints, interfaces, and acceptance criteria are closed. Save the approved design to `docs/rods/specs/YYYY-MM-DD-<topic>-design.md` only after the user confirms it. If the user says `ignorar planejamento do rods`, continue with a concise plan and record that opt-out.
